main_body:
Every application for the right to import lodged in accordance with Regulation (EC) No 1143/98 shall be granted to the following extent:
(a) for importers covered by Article 2(1)(a) of Regulation (EC) No 1143/98, 100 % of the quantities imported during the period 1 July 2001 to 30 June 2004;
(b) for importers covered by Article 2(1)(b) of Regulation (EC) No 1143/98, 23,7020 % of the quantities applied for.
